welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Terrytown, where southern hospitality meets small-town charm! Known for its rich history and vibrant culture, we invite you to explore our city and experience all it has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Lakefront Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Lakefront Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can access free WiFi throughout the airport.

airports.airport_name: Louis Armstrong New Orléans International Airport

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Louis Armstrong New Orléans International Airport houses the majority of the airport's services and amenities.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A at Louis Armstrong New Orléans International Airport primarily serves domestic flights operated by American Airlines and Delta Air Lines.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B at Louis Armstrong New Orléans International Airport primarily serves international flights operated by Southwest Airlines and Spirit Airlines.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network by selecting 'MSY Free WiFi' from the list of available networks.
